Insert into MESSAGES (SENDERID,RECIPIENTID,SUBJECT,DATE_SENT,MESSAGE_READ,TEXT) values (-2147483381,-2147483515,'Monty Python on Computer Interfaces',to_timestamp('04/11/01 16:33:15,000000000','DD/MM/RR HH24:MI:SS,FF'),'1','
                
                    
                


A: You Linux kids are so lucky. When we were using Windows 95 and Windows 3.11 
it kept getting stuck and we lost all our data. We had to reboot it.



